Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
read_instance_obs(25.10)                              read_instance_obs(25.10)

Name
       read_instance_obs  -  Allows importing the OD shape (cell LEF) informa-
       tion and writes it in the specified output file

Syntax
       read_instance_obs

       [-help]

       file

       Allows importing the OD shape (cell LEF) information and writes  it  in
       the specified output file.

       This  command  does not modify the design database while reading the OD
       shape information. If you modify the instance obstruction, the software
       updates the OD shape based on the current database.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes the  type  and  default
              information for each read_instance_obs parameter.

              For  a  detailed  description of the command and all its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man read_instance_obs

       file   Specifies the name of the output file for writing the  OD  shape
              information.

Related Information
              * add_cell_obs

              * delete_cell_obs

